\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {6}{\ignorespaces \textbf  {Inferred species richness over time across models.} Each panels shows the inferred number of cetacean lineages over time with a given model, conditioned on the reconstructed tree and recorded {\color  {blue} uncoded} occurrences. The gray line is the median value across the augmented trees in the combined MCMC samples from the 5 replicate analyses. The 5 overlapping black lines represent the lineage-through-time curves from the reconstructed phylogeny of each replicate. Dark and light yellow areas represent 50\% and 95\% credible intervals.\relax }}{21}{figure.caption.14}\protected@file@percent }
